<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Página no encontrada</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #d1e7dd, #a3cfbb);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .leaf-icon {
            display: inline-block;
            animation: bounce 1s infinite;
        }
        .recycle-icon {
            animation: spin 2s linear infinite;
        }
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        }
        @keyframes spin {
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        .btn-green {
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-green:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include ../views/layout/cabecera.ejs %>
    <div class="container d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center min-vh-100">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h1 class="display-1 fw-bold text-success mb-4">
                4<span class="fa fa-leaf"><i class="bi bi-leaf-fill"></i></span>4
            </h1>
            <h2 class="display-6 fw-semibold text-success mb-4">¡Oops! Página no encontrada</h2>
            <p class="lead text-success mb-5">
                Parece que la pagina que buscas no existe o aun no esta disponible!
            </p>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-success btn-lg rounded-pill btn-green">
                <i class="bi bi-house-door-fill me-2"></i>Volver al Inicio
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-5 text-success text-center">
            <p>Tip verde: Navegar menos páginas reduce tu huella de carbono digital. ¡Acabas de ahorrar energía!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>